title: Jove Multi-Mode Filter (Used)
description:
Bring the sound of Roland's Jupiter-6 to your rig. System 80's Jove is a no-nonsense and luscious analog filter and will bring the big man in the sky's astral grace to your modular setup.

Features:

4 modes: 24 dB low pass, 12 dB low pass, band pass and high pass
2 audio inputs, one log attenuated and one non-attenuated
2 frequency CV inputs, one unipolar input and one attenuverted input
1 resonance CV input, non-attenuated

This used unit is in excellent condition and comes with the original box.
